Output pr.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "setup-pr >/dev/null && cd /tmp/demo-repo && clear" Enter
Sleep 600ms
Show

Type "imp log"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "imp pr"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 7s

Enter
Sleep 5s
